---
title: Korean Ssamjang Veggie Fried Rice with Mayonnaise
description: We're channelling Korean flavours in this combination veggie fried rice. Sautéed sesame greens adds subtle
nuttiness and ssamjang paste provides the perfect amount of umami that play so well with everyone's finishing favourites... crispy shallots and a perfectly fried egg!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/korean-ssamjang-veggie-fried-rice-ea2ac05b.jpg
